(*) The number of reported cases for the last weeks may be incomplete.
**************************************************************
The Department of Heath is aggressively applying perifocal vector control
measures including insecticide spraying and reduction of mosquito breeding
sites. Awareness campaigns targeting at both the public and health
professionals are also regularly conducted.
